&lt;NEW&gt;

The mecha-lion continued to roar in pain as Trelos, rather than
relinquishing his bite on him, just bit down all the harder! However, rather
than letting go the armored cat also refused to give in. Setting his jaw he
attempted to use his large feline jaws and larger size to bowl Trelos over
and gain the advantage!

Around them the buildings echo with the sounds of thier battle, growls and
roars moving through the empty streets like tumbleweeds in some forgotten
town.

At the same time high overhead three blue jets with a definite Predacon
signature flew in a triangle formation from west to east over the cityscape.
The whistled slightly from the speed of thier passage, a triune contrail
tracing through the skies.They moved over the destetute nature of the city
like Eagles disrgarding carrion in search of greater prey. They had almost
passed over completely when majestically they broke formation and began to
circle back around, something had caught thier interest!

